<h5 id="subject_978216">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=107304.msg978216#msg978216" rel="nofollow">Re: 【GM手册-规则篇】5.可选战斗规则</a>
