<h5 id="subject_978217">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=107304.msg978217#msg978217" rel="nofollow">Re: 【GM手册-规则篇】5.可选战斗规则</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_978217'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_978217'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #4 于:</strong> 2019-02-20, 周三 22:37:24 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_978217_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
